text: The Church of All Saints is a Church of England parish church in the Uplands area of Stroud, Gloucestershire. The church is a Grade I listed building. It was designed by Temple Moore in the Gothic Revival style and was completed by Leslie Moore after Temple's death. ==References== ==External links== * Parish website * A Church Near You entry Stroud Stroud Stroud Category:20th-century Church of England church buildings
